":325349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3b57ba5075c2e58affde0d1d48040c6a43ae6c","tid":1842664,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df852feff0d54f163f5d74bfa4a23dfb135b11fe","tid":1842664,"uid":202972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a22581bd2c5bae13525130fa35915b80f2ab9ff9","tid":1842664,"uid":75597,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢點令你有對既感覺？<br />\n真係兩個人夾定係佢有啲咩做得好好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我之前啲男友都鍾意管我、有啲價值觀唔夾會成日嘈<br />\n而而家呢個佢好就我好錫我，但又唔係為左討好我冇晒主見果種<br />\n相處得好舒服<br />\n當然佢有時有啲野都會令我忟憎<br />\n之前去旅行已經嘈過幾鑊<br />\n但係我地都會好錫大家咁講返當時感受<br />\n如果火遮眼講野語氣重左都道返歉<br />\n總之係一種好平𧗾好舒服，唔洗點講都明對方諗乜既關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:26:26.000Z","msg":"哈 我都明白「好平衡」既感覺 <br />\n你哋拍咗幾耐啊？有plan結婚嗎？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T21:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048196525af08d12d1775bfaf1b7b53fcfe4a5b4","tid":1842664,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4535b86590d3ff8e887863b81802b9a42db64b9","tid":1842664,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4d831c67b5394226555938a1f2a9a07e741c64","tid":1842664,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3b57ba5075c2e58affde0d1d48040c6a43ae6c","tid":1842664,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T21:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T23:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c